article:
This is a 'list of wettest tropical cyclones by country,' using all known
available sources. Data is most complete for Australia, Cuba, the Dominican
Republic, Japan, Hong Kong, Mexico, Taiwan, Yap, Chuuk, and the United States,
with fragmentary data available for other countries. The French region of
RÃ©union holds several world records for tropical cyclone rainfall, due to the
rough topography and its proximity to the Indian ocean.
